{
  "stem": "24130.6",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they came-- civilian people came.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they taught us how to make a knot with, with cotton.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we couldn't figure out this-- it was a different way how to knot the cotton together.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then the next day, they took us to a factory.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this was a weaving factory where they made fabrics for the parachutes, white fabric.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So the fa-- the material was very thin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The cotton was very thin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So then we found out that you have to have good hands and good eyes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And for some reason, how much they looked, there were two girls that didn't have their fingers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "One didn't have two fingers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "One didn't have three fingers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it was terrible, because they were going to take them back to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My sister, Lilly, was very beautiful girl all the time-- tall, slim.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she, she was a very beautiful girl.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I guess the Germans just picked, you know, the stronger girls.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they were in charge on the, the-- she didn't go to the factory to work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She was in charge to keep the place clean.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And she had about six girls to help her to clean up the, the washroom.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We had to make our own beds, but to clean up the floors and the washroom.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Then we had a kitchen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Some girls worked in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So my sister was in charge.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And she was called the blockalteste.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when this girl, one of the girls didn't have the fingers-- so that she was with two other sisters.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they worked in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they came to my sister, Lilly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they says, you have to do something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because they want to take my sister, [INAUDIBLE], back to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
